<AbstractNarration>The objective valuation of the world's ecological systems and services and its natural capital stocks is an issue of global importance.  The proposed activity applies a functional modeling approach to collected information archives.  The resulting analysis tools should prove useful to a broad sector of the science and policy making community.  The proposed activities would lead to a web-based, publicly accessible resource for primary data storage and subsequent modeling for use in policy development as well as scientific research.</AbstractNarration>
